(thirdQuint)TREAT (Telemedicine for Reach, Education, Access, and Treatment).

 This study will assess whether a new care delivery model combining telemedicine videoconference diabetes consultations with diabetes self-management teaching is efficacious in reducing HbA1c in patients with type 2 diabetes in rural areas.

